*************************************************************
Terms & Conditions and Privacy Policy for Hue Feed Organizer
*************************************************************

The app named Hue Feed Organizer has been created as a free app. This app is provided by me at no cost and is intended for use as is.
The app is used to extract the dominant color of a picture, and to sort several pictures by hue, depending on their dominant color. External libraries are used
to perform this task. The execution is done on your local device, and it can vary depending on the specifications of your device.


The app and its creator are not responsible for any consequence that may affect your device, website, yourself or any other person or business 
after using the the app. 


You may not, whether by yourself or anyone on your behalf:
copy, modify, create derivative works of, adapt, emulate, translate, reverse engineer, compile, decompile or disassemble 
any portion of the content on the App and any other information, documents, material and data available 
on the App (collectively, the “Content”) in any way, or publicly display, perform, sell or distribute the Content, 
without our (the creator) prior written consent.


**** Privacy Policy ****

This is the privacy policy for the Hue Feed Organizer app.

Information Collection and Use:
The app does not require you to provide with personally identifiable information in order to be used. 
I do not sell, transfer or share any personal data to any third part. 

The app needs the write and read file permissions in order to be used. This is needed in order to access your app gallery where your pictures are stored.
The pictures that you load in this app will be stored in your local device only and they will be processed locally. 

The app does use third party services that may collect information used to identify you or your device.
The app includes AdMob in order to show personalized Ad banners. In particular, "Google can use the advertisment ID 
of the device where the Ad banner is shown, in order to generate interests and demographic data. 
The interests, the demographic data and other data can be used by Google to publish banner targeted for the user". 


The app does collect data for performance analytics purposes, such as approximate location, device ID, device model, operating system.

Remove your data and content:
I do not collect any personal data, therefore there will be no data to be removed from my side. If you have questions contact me at emavisuals@gmail.com.


Changes to This Privacy Policy:
I may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Thus, you are advised to review this page periodically for any changes. These changes are effective immediately after they are posted.

Contact Me:
If you have any questions or suggestions about my Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact me at emavisuals@gmail.com.

Latest update: 7 March 2022.
